A Proof Of Concept proving the best practice of orchestrating a CD with the trio SpringBoot-Gradle-Docker. Addition to
running a docker-compose project for running and configure Jenkins as Docker container project propose also a
dokerized provisioning of Jenkins jobs


Structure:

- simple springboot app > spring rest, spring persistence
- gradle configured for >  lifecycle, docker integration
- mysql integration
- flyway integration > using this cool db migration tool to initialize db